item.title: CVE-2023-2751|2024-08-02T06:33:05.263Z -- unknown -- upload%20resume
item.description: The Upload Resume WordPress plugin through 1.2.0 does not validate the captcha parameter when uploading a resume via the resume_upload_form shortcode, allowing unauthenticated visitors to upload arbitrary media files to the site.
